Step 2: Exploring / Information Gathering

Types of Questions

Open-ended Questions

 

•What will make this a successful meeting for you?

•What is your purchasing process?

•Please share a little about your process for investing in something like this.

•Who else besides yourself, is typically a part of this purchasing process?

•Tell me about your expectations regarding this solution.

Closed-ended Questions

 

•Does this sound good to you?

•Are you considering purchasing in the next two months?

•Would this have immediate benefit for you?

•Can I sign you up today?
